data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning two-story residence offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and practical comfort. With 3 bedrooms, an additional versatile office that can easily serve as a fourth bedroom, and an expansive open floor plan, this home is designed to meet all your lifestyle needs.    Step inside and be captivated by the spacious living areas, featuring not one, but three inviting living areas that provide ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Just one highlight of the home is the dedicated game room, providing the ideal setting for friendly gatherings or family game nights.    The well-appointed kitchen seamlessly integrates with the living areas, creating a harmonious flow for everyday living and entertaining. Two separate eating areas, including a separate dining space and a casual breakfast nook, offer versatility for any dining occasion.    No detail has been overlooked in the design of this home, with a commitment to elegance and easy maintenance. The absence of carpet throughout ensures a clean and allergy-friendly environment, while also adding a touch of sophistication.    Escape to the outdoors to a generous backyard retreat. The large patio provides the perfect setting for al fresco dining, weekend barbecues, or simply unwinding in the fresh air. The spacious yard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities and landscaping customization.    Conveniently located in a desirable neighborhood, this residence is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Close to schools, parks, shopping, and dining, you'll enjoy the perfect combination of tranquility and accessibility.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a viewing today and discover the endless possibilities that await you in this meticulously designed and thoughtfully crafted residence.
